The corresponding impulse response is a rectangular pulse, and the frequency response is

\[H(e^{j\omega})\,=\,\frac{1}{N\,+\,M\,+\,1}\,e^{j\omega\left[(N\,-\,M\,)/2\right]} \,\frac{\sin[\omega(M\,+\,N\,+\,1)/2]}{\sin(\omega/2)}. \tag{6.79}\]

